overview: Fritte Söderström's latest Jante video, focusing on various cities throughout Sweden. Featuring Gustav Tønnesen, Nisse Ingemarsson, Martin Sandberg, Vincent Huhta, Josef Scott Jatta, Filip Almqvist, Simon Hallberg, Eric Hedberg, Axel Berggren, Kinser Cathey, Hannes Edvinsson, Koffe Hallgren, Alex Elfving, Oscar Säfström & Ville Rockäng.
title: Jante - 11:00
